<item>
            <title>[LU-19025] ldlm_completion_ast() may never timeout, even without NO_TIMEOUT</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19025</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ldlm_completion_ast() may never timeout, even without NO_TIMEOUT. One of the waits in this function has no timeout. A previous version of Lustre had timeouts on both waits.&lt;/p&gt;

